item.title: 30 Day Challenges: May 25 - June 24
item.description: I’m 29 year old now, I has been working as a software engineer for more than seven years. And you know; this is my third company that I’m been working during my whole career, I got some quite interviews still now. I had to admit that I’m not a really good software engineer, I don’t have a deep knowledge to what I’m been working on. One reason would be impatience and didn’t spend more time on researching things.
